06:09.068 --> 06:12.029
- Who's there?
- Me. Who's there?

06:14.865 --> 06:17.701
- Coach?
- No, I'm Coach.

06:22.331 --> 06:26.586
- What are you doing here, Coach?
- At least we got that straight.

06:26.753 --> 06:31.508
We almost had the most incredible
disaster. Look at this TV guide.

06:33.385 --> 06:35.428
"Thunder Road".

06:35.595 --> 06:41.602
Mitchum. We haven't missed a Mitchum
