06:41.769 --> 06:46.858
- We don't wanna miss the beginning.
- Mitchum won't start without us.

06:47.942 --> 06:51.696
- We're gonna need munchies.
- Diane's got some.

06:51.863 --> 06:58.244
While you're up, turn down the lights.
There's a terrible glare on the screen.

07:15.304 --> 07:17.348
Take me, you barbarian.

07:21.311 --> 07:24.063
You're gonna miss "Thunder Road".

07:27.108 --> 07:32.071
