- Nothing yet. They're going up the road.

07:32.238 --> 07:35.784
No, with Diane.
Hey, Diane, you all right?

07:39.663 --> 07:41.957
What is Coach doing here?

07:42.124 --> 07:47.880
He's watching "Thunder Road". We
always watch Mitchum movies together.

07:48.964 --> 07:51.635
It's a bad time right now.

07:51.801 --> 07:56.348
I know, but it's a tradition
