08:13.074 --> 08:15.117
What?

08:17.870 --> 08:20.331
- What's wrong?
- Sam.

08:21.540 --> 08:25.170
- A little tact.
- I'm sorry. Coach, listen.

08:25.337 --> 08:27.381
What?

08:27.547 --> 08:31.426
