08:43.523 --> 08:47.485
Diane, forgive me. I never
wanted to get in your way.

08:47.652 --> 08:49.779
Thank you for understanding.

08:49.946 --> 08:54.659
When you live alone,
you forget other people have lives.

09:00.916 --> 09:06.713
