10:18.372 --> 10:21.834
Or if I don't like their attitudes,
I can spit in it.

10:30.052 --> 10:34.306
You're not still upset about that argument
we had the other day?

10:34.473 --> 10:36.516
You tell me.

10:49.238 --> 10:54.494
I'm sorry about this morning
when I called you a sawed-off witch.

11:07.049 --> 11:13.055
