me before we became a threesome.

11:13.222 --> 11:15.266
Yes, I recognise you now.

11:15.433 --> 11:18.937
- You shaved off your Pantusso.
- That's it.

11:22.148 --> 11:25.235
- I know.
- I can't take it any more.

11:25.402 --> 11:31.199
- We never go anyplace without Coach.
- I don't invite him. He just shows up.

11:31.366 --> 11:36.080
- What are we gonna do?
