11:45.673 --> 11:51.138
Coach, I'm sorry. I overslept.
We were up late last night watching...

11:51.304 --> 11:56.685
- "Mothra Versus Godzilla".
- Was I disappointed in that.

11:58.311 --> 12:05.318
We've got to draw the line. No way
can we spend the evening with Coach.

12:05.485 --> 12:08.114
You're absolutely right.

12:08.281 --> 12:11.576
Are we gonna get together tonight?

12:11.742 --> 12:15.621
- You bet.
- Great.

12:17.874 --> 12:22.128
All right. There's only one solution
to this problem.

12:22.295 --> 12:26.925
We have to tell the Coach
