14:11.369 --> 14:15.999
Is there one I should talk to?
Friendly, nice, cute?

14:16.165 --> 14:18.209
Frank.

14:18.376 --> 14:21.379
Who's the one you always talk to?

14:21.546 --> 14:24.633
Redhead with a nice smile
