No, not Stella.
I'm not too crazy about Stella.

15:00.588 --> 15:03.924
- I meant Dorothy.
- Yes, so did I.

15:05.009 --> 15:09.138
- Dorothy is the one you like, right?
- She's very nice.

15:09.305 --> 15:10.723
Excuse me.

15:13.184 --> 15:16.438
