20:50.383 --> 20:53.803
- Over and over again.
- You really were a drunk.

20:53.970 --> 20:56.014
I know.

20:56.181 --> 21:00.060
- I mean, you were really a drunk.
- Don't start again.

21:00.268 --> 21:06.191
