come out tell each other the truth?

21:09.277 --> 21:11.822
You're right.

21:11.988 --> 21:15.910
We just don't want you
hanging around us so much.

21:21.124 --> 21:24.711
If you don't want me, it's fine.
I'm not mad.

21:24.877 --> 21:29.674
It's fine. I'll see you.

21:32.469 --> 21:34.513
But you really were a drunk.

21:50.697 --> 21:53.950
- Morning, Norm.
- Where the heck have you been?

21:54.117 --> 21:58.663
- Is my watch fast?
- Sorry. We had a difficult evening.

21:58.830 --> 22:03.209
We had to tell Coach
we didn't want to see him any more.

22:03.376 --> 22:06.255
